    {
      "instruction": "<p>Pat your <strong>haddock bites</strong> dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Tip: Unevenly sized haddock bites? Chop any larger ones into bite-sized pieces!</p><p>Add the <strong>haddock bites </strong>to a bowl with your <strong>chipotle paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and give them a good mix until the fish is nicely coated</p>",
